BR_text.BRsummary: Input and output data to shufflenet v2 have incorrect shapes
BR_text.BRdescription:
<denchmark-h:h1>Bug Report</denchmark-h>
 
 <denchmark-h:h3>Which model does this pertain to?</denchmark-h>
 
 shufflenet v2
 <denchmark-h:h3>Describe the bug</denchmark-h>
 
 Input and output .pb files have incorrect shapes (they don't have batch dimension).
 Eg. model requires input with shape (1, 3, 224, 224), while input_0.pb has shape (3, 224, 224).
 Similar issue with output_0.pb - model requires (1, 1000), output_0.pb has shape (1000,)
